verbose_text: Given that phenotypic suppression by RNase H overexpression is accepted as a marker for R-loops, these results suggest that the suppression of hpr1Delta sen1-3 by overexpression of RNH1 might occur by removing short or labile DNA : RNA hybrids, not readily detectable by the S9.6 antibody used in our analysis.
evidence: suppression of hpr1Delta sen1-3 by overexpression of RNH1
